{"tid":1374980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[大大大力推] 今日岀上環既巴絲一定要睇！！！","createTime":"2019-07-28T02:42:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T03:36:16.000Z","uid":27739,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c0ea10357015cbdc893c68399277640eeab9247b","tid":1374980,"uid":27739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:42:27.000Z","msg":"經過琴日一役之後 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對面一定會揾辦法去爭取返民意 <br />\n<br />\n所以今日岀上環既巴絲<br />\n<br />\n真係要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">小心有黑底人仕滲入  </span></span><br />\n<br />\n琴日元朗啲鄉黑都冇做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以今日佢地岀黎既機會大好多<br />\n<br />\n如果見到佢地想<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">破壞周邊既商店</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一定要岀手<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">阻止 </span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為係呢個時候輿論戰係好重要既一環<br />\n<br />\n唔好比佢地有機可乘！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 ， 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"35fc1633e46d3f9d520449aa46a0080c71a07ee6","tid":1374980,"uid":27739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:42:44.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e0f9a6b6927b863ee6be436522eac349c4f2ad","tid":1374980,"uid":27739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:42:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=